{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place bread in mixing bowl and grind <nobr>5 sec\/speed 7<\/nobr>. Transfer to a large bowl and set aside.","Place parsley, spring onion and garlic in mixing bowl then chop <nobr>3 sec\/speed 7<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add butterbeans, lemon juice, flour, cumin, salt and egg then blend <nobr>5 sec\/speed 7<\/nobr>. Transfer to bowl with breadcrumbs.","Add crumbled feta to breadcrumb mix and stir in with spatula. Tip out and and shape into 4 equal-sized patties. Place on a plate, cover with cling film and place in fridge for 1 hour. Towards the end of this time, light barbecue or preheat grill (220°C)","Cook burgers on barbecue or under grill (220°C) until completely browned on one side (approx. 6-8 minutes). Carefully loosen from grill bars using a palette knife or spatula then flip over and cook other side until golden brown and cooked through. Serve in burger buns with coleslaw and chips if desired."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"Burgers","content":["50 g bread","5 sprigs fresh flat-leaf parsley, leaves only","1 spring onion, cut in pieces","½ garlic clove","240 g tinned butter beans (1 x 400 g tin, drained weight approx. 240 g)","10 g lemon juice","1 Tbsp plain flour","1 tsp ground cumin","½ tsp fine sea salt","1 egg, medium","100 g feta cheese, crumbled"]},{"title":"To Serve","content":["4 burger buns","coleslaw"]}],"id":"r97065","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-4385npCsS18\/XZVRTMZRoXI\/AAAAAAAAdMk\/jEVJC3sWT6oqd7raj7btcOV3FTPxpwN1gCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_lAUT2fRnAxufC7BQ.png","title":"Butterbean and Feta Burgers","publishedAt":"2016-05-30T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"11 g","fat":"7.4 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"17.6 g","calories":"755 kJ \/ 181 kcal"},"usefulItems":"cling film, palette knife, refrigerator, grill","basicInfo":["easy","25m","1h 30m","4 portions"]}